text: Gilbert Raynes (21 August 1903 - July 1986) was a British gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1986 deaths Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wolverhampton
